<p>The final surface base to be constructed as part of the Colonia Expansion Initiative, Karrison's Landing was established by the Nomads of Nevermore on a distant outer moon of this system. An industrial base, producing a wide range of basic goods, its distant location avoids potential interference with the native life on the Earthlike in the inner system.</p>
<p>The Nomads, as their name implies, are originally from the Nevermore system in the bubble, though nowadays have little presence there.</p>
